To start the app:
  python src/app.py

To run the APP UT:
  python test/test_app.py

This test generates curl.sh, which can be run:
  bash curl.sh

To test the routing mechanism:
  python test/test_router.py




The app is currently deployed on Heroku, to test:

python test/test_app.py --host https://rocky-forest-8535.herokuapp.com

There is an extra "GET /" which allows verifying that the app is up.
